        <Parent_String>writing equipment [300404590], drafting, drawing and writing equipment by specific type [300168215], equipment for drafting, drawing, and writing [300168214], image-making equipment [300162803], equipment by process [300024659], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hand-held board-like objects used for writing or drawing, either written upon directly or used as a support for paper or another material. For artifacts rather than equipment, particularly artifacts upon which something has been written, use "writing tablets (information artifacts)." For larger boards for writing, use "writing boards (writing equipment)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000093897/Metropolitan Museum of Art [online] (2001-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Met de hand vastgehouden bordachtige voorwerpen, ofwel om direct op te schrijven of tekenen, ofwel als ondersteuning voor papier of ander materiaal. Gebruik 'schrijftabletten (informatiedragers)' wanneer het niet benodigdheden maar artefacten betreft, met name als hierop iets is geschreven. Gebruik 'schrijfborden' voor grotere borden om op te schrijven.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
